data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS on the property. Please submit your highest and best offer  by 11/8/21 6 PM  Seller will review and decide  by 11/9 /21 . Gorgeous 3 Bedroom plus den/office in a well established neighborhood in Lehigh Acres. The property is under construction to be complete middle late January 2022. Top quality and design home with plenty of upgrades. Hight interior ceiling with 9'4" in bedrooms, 11'0" in living room area and 12'0" tray ceiling. Ceramic tile throughout the house. Granite Type II in kitchen and bathrooms. Modern cabinets shaker style with soft close doors. The house has HURRICANE IMPACT WINDOWS AND SLIDING DOOR. Beautiful stainless steel appliances. At this stage of the construction you can pick some finishes. Pictures and video tour from previous home. Some colors or finishes maybe different in base of supply Please check the video tour
